Maybe not for this PR, but consider Qq-ifing `synthesizeUsingTactic'` too.
Indeed, that already crossed my mind; though I figured that would have a larger fallout and was best left to a follow up.
Is there a reason to prefer this over `synthInstanceQ`?
Yes, this version does the instance search (from the local `Field Î±`) at compile time rather than each time the tactic is run.
